{"success":true,"data":{"markdown":"[Skip to content](https://www.dangpestcontrol.com/about/#content)\n\n# Why Choose Us/Meet The Team\n\n# about us\n\n![Kirk and Claire - Owners of Dang Pest Control](https://www.dangpestcontrol.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Kirk-and-Claire.jpg)\n\n#### About us\n\nWe have been in the home services industry for over 15 years and love that our contribution to you is to bring peace and security to a place where you should feel the safest. At [Dang Pest Control](https://www.dangpestcontrol.com/), we are a hands-on, personable, relationship-based, and family-owned company. We live, work, worship, and play in the Tyler community.\n\nOur [innovative pest control practices](https://www.dangpestcontrol.com/pest-control/) help us stand out amongst our competitors. Our goal is to be an active part in making our community and the lives of our clients better. We promise fun, enjoyable interactions with clients while providing reliable and professional service every step of the way – from our fast communication practices to our extensive pest control plans. We stand by our work and guarantee satisfaction.\n\n[(903) 871-0550](tel:(903)%20871-0550)\n\n[Get Your Quote](https://www.dangpestcontrol.com/quote/)\n\n![Cloud Image](https://www.dangpestcontrol.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Longview.png)\n\n## Expertise & Proven Results\n\nAt Dang Pest Control, we pride ourselves on expertise, proven results, and a customer-first approach.\n\nOur trained professionals use the latest Integrated Pest Management methods to protect your home or business while prioritizing your family and pets. With reliable service, fast response times, and a commitment to long-term prevention, we’re the trusted choice for pest control in East Texas.\nWhen hiring a pest control company, it’s important to look for a team that is licensed, experienced, and committed to effective treatments. We offer customized solutions based on your specific pest problem, use environmentally 